rators?</span></h2> <p>A: Yup! It's much easier if you come to us about it, and it gives you the control over what you want shown on the news page.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong>« <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-10-2020">October 2020</a> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-11-2020">November 2020</a></span> | <a class="newpage" href="http://www.scpwiki.com/news-12-2020">December 2020</a> »</strong></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <hr /> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251540" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-755619-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. with a rating above 0</div> </div> 
