				<title>Underread and Underrated October 2020</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/uau102020</link>
				<description>

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;« &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/uau92020&quot;&gt;September 2020&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/uau102020&quot;&gt;October 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/uau112020&quot;&gt;November 2020&lt;/a&gt; »&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;feature-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;content-panel left-column&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Featured SCP!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3687&quot;&gt;SCP-3687&lt;/a&gt;: Anti-Entropy Doorknobs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A note inside of a fireproof lock-box was discovered in Mr. Hannigan&#039;s bedroom, reading: &amp;quot;Finally, I&#039;ve done it. Here, you can have this one.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-footer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Featured SCP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;content-panel right-column&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Featured Tale/Format!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/unicorn-crackfic-procedures&quot;&gt;Unicorn Crackfic Procedures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;quot;Let me be honest. After you see some biped on your best unicorn&#039;s back, using its pale little digits to violate his haunches, you stop caring about the ethics of the H-class.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-footer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Featured non-SCP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#32;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;Topic and Prompt of the month!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-folded&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;+&amp;nbsp;Open&amp;nbsp;FAQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded&quot; style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-unfolded-link&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:150%;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;collapsible-block-link&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;FAQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;what&#039;s this?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Underread and Underrated is a project intended to shine a spotlight on, well, underread and underrated pages!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;oh neat. What&#039;s the blurb for?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the associated UaU initiative, each month we&#039;ll be picking an element of SCP lore that people outside the general gestalt might not know about. We&#039;re also hosting writing challenges involving said lore!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;may i suggest [blank] for the topic?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sure! Do note, however, that anything with a dedicated hub&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-588838-1&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; above +100 in rating can&#039;t be made topic. Sorry! D:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suggestions should be PM&#039;d to &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610251541&quot; alt=&quot;UraniumEmpire&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;UraniumEmpire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;oh cool how do i participate?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just PM &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610251541&quot; alt=&quot;UraniumEmpire&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;UraniumEmpire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; a link to your piece and she&#039;ll post it on next month&#039;s &amp;quot;Last Month&#039;s Pieces and Topic&amp;quot; section!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For artists: try to link to whatever social media page is hosting the art. It saves us space and ensures we have a solid reference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;content-panel centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Last Month&#039;s Pieces and Topic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/fault-lines&quot;&gt;Fault Lines&lt;/a&gt; and the Gulf canon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-footer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The best of the past.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;content-panel centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-heading&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic + pick of this month!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-body&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scpwiki.com/new-age-hub&quot;&gt;New Age&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;panel-footer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This month&#039;s piece.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New Age is a novel-length trilogy about the Chaos Insurgency. It&#039;s a bit of a long read, so let&#039;s not worry too much about the description, alright?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;This month&#039;s challenge:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For writers:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8230; why don&#039;t you take a break for this one? It&#039;s a long read.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For artists:&lt;/strong&gt; And if you feel inspired to draw a scene from it afterwards&amp;#8230; well, the more the merrier!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;by &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610251541&quot; alt=&quot;UraniumEmpire&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;UraniumEmpire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;footnotes-footer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Footnotes&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;footnote-footer&quot; id=&quot;footnote-588838-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:;&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;. Meaning a hub dedicated exclusively or primarily to the topic. GoI Formats would &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; count unless the primary content for the GoI is its formats.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
